OL,3,CLower speed limits introduced on
OL,4,C'dangerous' road where two people were
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FNew speed limits have been introduced
OL,8,Fon a six-mile stretch of the A38 in
OL,9,FCornwall, where two people were killed
OL,10,Fin five years.
OL,12,FThe changes are part of a major road
OL,13,Fsafety initiative aimed at reducing
OL,14,Fcasualties on one of the county's
OL,15,Fbusiest routes.
