OL,3,CLower speed limits introduced on
OL,4,C'dangerous' road where two people were
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FFrom today (Wednesday 20th August)
OL,8,Fmotorists travelling through the
OL,9,Fvillages of Tideford and Landrake will
OL,10,Fbe restricted to 30mph, down from the
OL,11,Fprevious 40mph limit, with enforcement
OL,12,Fprovided by two new spot speed cameras.
OL,14,FThe #750,000 safety scheme is being
OL,15,Fdelivered by National Highways in
OL,16,Fpartnership with Cornwall Council and
OL,17,FDevon & Cornwall Police.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
