OL,3,CLower speed limits introduced on
OL,4,C'dangerous' road where two people were
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FLatest data show that between 2019 and
OL,8,F2023, 60 crashes happened on this
OL,9,Fsection of road, resulting in 97
OL,10,Fcasualties and two fatalities.
OL,12,FNational Highways said: "Research
OL,13,Fdemonstrates a direct correlation
OL,14,Fbetween speed, collision frequency and
OL,15,Fseverity, with the risk of serious
OL,16,Finjury or death increasing
OL,17,Fsignificantly even with minor speed
OL,18,Fincreases."
OL,20,FIn the area, there's been mixed
OL,21,Freaction to the lower speed limits.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
