OL,3,CLower speed limits introduced on
OL,4,C'dangerous' road where two people were
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FOne woman said, "I think it causes
OL,8,Fmore tail backs and more issues, I
OL,9,Fdon't think it's a dangerous road,
OL,10,Fthere's no need."
OL,12,FOne man added:"We are all about
OL,13,Fsafety, but I've got a business and
OL,14,Fit's a bit of a nightmare and it's all
OL,15,Fabout finances, and really they're
OL,16,Fgoing to be making a lot of money off
OL,17,Fworking people."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
