OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FAnother local said: "It's alright, if
OL,8,Feveryone drives at the speed limit,
OL,9,Fbut if people slow down it will make
OL,10,Fothers irate."
OL,12,FBut campaigner for Safe A38, David
OL,13,FLanders said the new speed limit is
OL,14,Fneeded: "Any extra safety measures
OL,15,Finstalled along this stretch are
OL,16,Fwelcomed, it is one of the most
OL,17,Fdangerous stretches on the A38.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
