OL,3,CLower speed limits introduced on
OL,4,C'dangerous' road where two people were
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,F"When you know people who have
OL,8,Fsuffered a loss on this road, you take
OL,9,Fit seriously, it's been a long process
OL,10,Fbut we have got there eventually, at
OL,11,Fleast with the speed limit."
OL,13,FHe added: "The killed and seriously
OL,14,Finjured rate is three times higher
OL,15,Fthan the average for the country."
OL,17,FThe speed reduction follows the recent
OL,18,Fcompletion of work to install ten
OL,19,Faverage speed cameras managing the
OL,20,Fexisting 50mph limit between Carkeel
OL,21,Froundabout and Trerulefoot.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
