OL,3,CLower speed limits introduced on
OL,4,C'dangerous' road where two people were
OL,5,Ckilled
OL,7,FJack Mason, National Highways' South
OL,8,FWest Road Safety Manager, said: "We
OL,9,Fdid a comparison between this section
OL,10,Fof the A38 and found that there was
OL,11,Fabout a 50% higher collision rate on
OL,12,Fthis section compared to other similar
OL,13,FNational Highway's roads, so it made
OL,14,Fsense for us to intervene and put
OL,15,Fthese safety measures in."
